* Prince Ardeshir Mirza &quot;Rokn ed-Dowleh&quot;
* Prince Ahmad Mirza &quot;Mo&#x27;in ed-Dowleh&quot;
* Prince Ja&#x27;far Gholi Mirza
* Prince Mostafa Gholi Mirza
* Prince Hesam o-Saltaneh, Morad Mirza
